    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "That was a big, big money.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "No, when I was in Canada, I take the-- the relatives gave me some things-- clothes, what I-- I was in the flea markets.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I was looking, and I bought something-- stuff, and I brought to Russia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And we sold the stuff, and we make [INAUDIBLE] the money.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Then beg-- begin-- we decided to go out from Russia to Canada.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Our son, the younger, the [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Dialdo ?] the son, he finished university at-- in English, Russian language.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "The other son, he was-- [INAUDIBLE] in that time, he started university at [INAUDIBLE] [? irrigation. ?] And he finished, and we talked with the wife let him-- we will go-- let him not finish the [?university?].",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "No, how-- maybe we'll need to feel better when he will finish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "No, we decide he will finish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And we stayed a couple years after that, when they came from-- in the 1970-- 1976, we begin to send-- give the papers for come out from Russia.",
